column.name: Query
column.value: "SELECT prop.id as id_proposta, prop.sequencial || '/' || prop.ano as nr_proposta, prop.ano as ano_proposta, to_char(cast(siconv.dt_envio_proposta(prop.id) as date),'DD/MM/YYYY') as dt_envio_proposta, case when prop.inicio_execucao isnull then '01/01/1900' else to_char(prop.inicio_execucao,'DD/MM/YYYY') end as dt_inic_vigenc_proposta, case when prop.fim_execucao isnull then '01/01/1900' else to_char(prop.fim_execucao,'DD/MM/YYYY') end as dt_fim_vigenc_proposta, case when prop.data_proposta isnull then '01/01/1900' else to_char(prop.data_proposta,'DD/MM/YYYY') end as dt_cadastro_proposta, case when prop.objeto_convenio is null then 'NÃO INFORMADO' else prop.objeto_convenio end as tx_desc_objeto_proposta, case when prop.justificativa is null then 'NÃO INFORMADO' else prop.justificativa end as tx_desc_justific_proposta, case when prop.valor_contrapartida_bens_servi > '0' then '1' else 2 end as id_ind_contrapartida_bens, case when in_ges.prop_fk isnull then 2 else 1 end as id_ind_parecer_gestor, case when in_jur.prop_fk isnull then 2 else 1 end as id_ind_parecer_juridico, case when in_tec.prop_fk isnull then 2 else 1 end as id_ind_parecer_tecnico, case when age.agencia isnull then 'NÃO INFORMADO' else age.agencia end as nr_agencia_dv, case when age.banco_fk isnull then '-8' else age.banco_fk end as id_banco, case when prog.programa_fk isnull then '-8' else prog.programa_fk end as id_programa, case when prop.proponente_fk isnull then '-8' else prop.proponente_fk end as id_proponente, case when org.id isnull then '-8' else org.id end as id_orgao_concedente, case when prop.modalidade isnull then '-8' else prop.modalidade end as id_modalidade, siconv.replace_situacao_prop_dw(prop.id) as id_situacao_proposta, case when prop.membro_partc_fk is null then '-8' else prop.membro_partc_fk end as id_pessoa_resp_cadastro, case when siconv.resp_envio_prop_dw(prop.id) is null then '-8' else siconv.resp_envio_prop_dw(prop.id) end as id_pessoa_resp_envio, case when rconv.membro_fk is null then '-8' else rconv.membro_fk end as id_pessoa_resp_concedente, prop.valor_global as vl_global, prop.valor_repasse as vl_repasse, prop.valor_contra_partida as vl_contrapartida_total, prop.valor_contrapartida_financeira as vl_contrapartida_financeira, prop.valor_contrapartida_bens_servi as vl_contrapartida_bens, case when conv.numero_processo isnull then '-9' else conv.numero_processo end as nr_processo, case when cont.conta is null then '-8' else cont.conta end as nr_conta_corrente from siconv.prop prop LEFT JOIN siconv.objeto obj ON obj.id = prop.objeto_fk LEFT JOIN siconv.prop_programa prog ON prog.prop_fk = prop.id LEFT JOIN siconv.org_administrativo org ON org.id = prop.org_concedente_fk LEFT JOIN siconv.conta_bancaria cont ON cont.prop_fk = prop.id LEFT JOIN siconv.age_bancaria age on cont.age_entity_fk = age.id LEFT JOIN siconv.convenio conv on prop.convenio_fk = conv.id LEFT JOIN (select distinct ppc1.prop_fk from siconv.parecer_prop_convenio ppc1 where ppc1.atribuicao_responsavel like '%Gestor%') in_ges on prop.id = in_ges.prop_fk LEFT JOIN (select distinct ppc1.prop_fk from siconv.parecer_prop_convenio ppc1 where ppc1.atribuicao_responsavel like '%Jurídico%') in_jur on prop.id = in_jur.prop_fk LEFT JOIN (select distinct ppc1.prop_fk from siconv.parecer_prop_convenio ppc1 where ppc1.atribuicao_responsavel like '%Técnico%') in_tec on prop.id = in_tec.prop_fk LEFT JOIN siconv.responsaveis_convenio rconv on (prop.id = rconv.prop_fk and prop.org_concedente_fk = rconv.concedente_fk) "
